<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Récapitulatif de votre contrat</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #0f52ba;
            --secondary-color: #4a89dc;
            --accent-color: #e74c3c;
            --success-color: #2ecc71;
            --light-bg: #f8fafc;
            --dark-bg: #1a365d;
            --text-color: #334155;
            --light-text: #f1f5f9;
            --border-radius: 10px;
            --box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --transition: all 0.25s ease;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 25px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, var(--dark-bg), var(--primary-color));
            color: var(--light-text);
            padding: 35px 30px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .header-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .document-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-left: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 35px 30px;
        }

        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 6px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

        .card-title i {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .contract-details {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .detail-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
            padding: 14px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            align-items: center;
        }

        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }

        .detail-row:first-child {
            padding-top: 0;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            padding-right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .detail-label i {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            width: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .detail-value {
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-family: 'SF Pro Display', 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .detail-row:hover .detail-value {
            background-color: #e9f0fd;
            border-color: rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .important {
            margin-top: 25px;
            background-color: rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.08);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.15);
        }

        .important::before {
            content: "\f05a";
            font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .contact-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.2);
        }

        .contact-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(74, 137, 220, 0.3);
        }

        .contact-button i {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--light-bg), #f1f5f9);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #64748b;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .company-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .company-logo {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .container {
                margin: 0;
            }

            .header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 20px;
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .document-icon {
                margin-left: 0;
                align-self: center;
            }

            .detail-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 8px;
                padding: 16px 0;
            }

            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>Récapitulatif de votre contrat</h1>
            <p>Merci pour votre confiance. Voici les détails de votre abonnement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="document-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p class="intro-text">Un petit récapitulatif des informations de votre contrat :</p>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">
                <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i> Détails de votre contrat
            </div>

            <div class="contract-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Prestation :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.prestation }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-sync"></i> Récurrence :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.reccurence }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-calendar-plus"></i> Date de création :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.createdAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> Date du premier paiement :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.firstPaymentAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i> Date du prochain paiement :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.nextPaymentAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-percent"></i> TVA applicable :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.tva }}%</div>
                </div>

                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> Coût annuel :</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{ websiteContract.monthlyCost|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="important">Si vous avez des questions concernant ce contrat, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.</p>

        <a href="#contact" class="contact-button">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Nous contacter
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Cordialement,<br>L'équipe de MyRocket</p>

        <div class="company-info">
            <div class="company-logo">
                <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
            </div>
            <span>MyRocket</span>
        </div>

        <div class="copyright">
            © 2025 MyRocket - Tous droits réservés
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>